snippet.title: Amber Heard partners with SAMS to launch PSS program for Syrian refugee women in Lebanon
snippet.description:
Last February, Amber partnered with SAMS in a missionary trip to Lebanon where she visited refugee camps. Together, they're launching a PSS program for Syrian refugee women. Please, donate at this link: https://www.crowdrise.com/o/en/campaign/amberheardlebanon
